hadiths[42]{hadithnumber,text}:
948,umr (Raziallahu anhu) aik motey reshamii kapdey ka chogha lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey jo bazar mein bik raha tha kehney lagey : ya Rasulullah! aap isey khareed lijiye aur eid ke mauqon par aur bahar se milne k liye aaney walon k saamne isey pahan kar zeenat farmaya keejiye. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to wo pahney ga jiska ( aakhirat mein) koi hissey nahi. iske baad jab tak Allah ne chaha umr rahi phir aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud unke paas aik reshamii chogha tohfe mein bhejaa. umr (Raziallahu anhu) usey liye huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! aap ne to ye farmaya ke usko wo pahnega jiska aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi phir aap ne ye mere paas kyon bhejaa? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine usey terey pahnney ko nahi bheja balke isliye ke tum usey bech kar uski qeemat apne kaam mein laao.
949,aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere ghar tashrif laey us waqt mere paas (ansaar ki) 2 ladkiyan jange-Bua'aas ke qisson ki nazmein padh rahi thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bistar par let gaey aur apna chehra dusri taraf pher liya. iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur mujhey daantaa aur farmaya ke ye shaitaanii baajaa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maujoodgii mein? aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya ke janey do khamosh raho phir jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) doosrey kaam mein lag gaey to maine unhein ishara kya aur wo chali gaiin.
950,aur ye eid ka din tha. Habsha ke kuchh log dhaalon aur barchhiyon se khel rahe they. ab khud maine kaha ya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tum ye khel dekho gii ? maine kaha ji haan. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey apne peechhey khada kar liya. mera rukhsar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rukhsar par tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they khelo-khelo aey bani arfada ye Habsha ke logon ka laqab tha phir jab main thak gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' bas!'' maine kaha ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao .
951,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne eid ke din khutba detey huey farmaya ke pahlaa kaam jo ham aaj ke din (eidul-azhaa) mein kartey hain, ye hai ke pahley ham Namaz padhein phir wapas aa kar qurbani karein. jisne is tarah kya wo hamarey tareeq par chalaa."
952,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laey to mere paas Ansar ki 2 ladkiyan wo ashaar ga rahi thin jo Ansar ne Buaas ki jang ke mauqe par kahey they. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke ye gaaney waaliyaan nahi thin, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar mein ye shaitaanii baajey aur ye eid ka din tha aakhir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya aey abu-Bakar! har qaum ki eid hoti hai aur aaj ye hamari eid hai."
953,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-fitr ke din na nikaltey jab tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chand khajoorein na kha letey aur Murji-bin-Rijaa ne kaha ke mujh se Ubaidullah -bin-abi-Bakr ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujh se Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, phir yahi hadis bayan ki ke aap taaq adad khajoorein khaatey they."
954,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs Namaz se pahley qurbani kar de usey dobara karni chahiye is par aik shakhs (abu-Barda) ne khadey ho kar kaha ke ye aisa din hai jis mein gosht ki khahish zyada hoti hai aur usne apne padausiyon ki tangi ka haal bayan kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko sachcha samjha us shakhs ne kaha ke mere paas aik saal ki pathiya hai jo gosht ki 2 bakriyon se bhi mujhey zyada pyari hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par usey ijazat de di ke wahi qurbani kare. ab mujhey malum nahi ke ye ijazat dusron ke liye bhi hai ya nahi.
955,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne eidul-Azha ki Namaz ke baad khutba detey huey farmaya ke jis shakhs ne hamari Namaz ki tarah Namaz padhi aur hamari qurbani ki tarah qurbani ki uski qurbani sahi hui lekin jo shakhs Namaz se pahley qurbani karey wo Namaz se pahley hi gosht khata hai magar wo qurbani nahi. Bara ke maamun abu-barda-bin-Niyaar ye sun kar boley ke ya Rasulullah ! maine apni bakri ki qurbani Namaz se pahley kar di, maine sochaa ke ye khaaney-peeney ka din hai meri bakri agar ghar ka pahlaa zabiha baney to bahut achchha ho. us khayal se maine bakri zabah kar di aur Namaz se pahley hi iska gosht bhi kha liya. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tumhari bakri gosht ki bakri hui. abu-Barda bin-Niyaar ne arz kya ke mere paas aik saal ki pathiya hai aur wo mujhey gosht ki 2 bakriyon se bhi azeez hai, kya us se meri qurbani ho jaeygi? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan lekin tumharey baad kisi ki qurbani us Umr ke bachchey se kafi na hogi."
956,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-fitr aur eidul-Azha ke din (Madina ke bahar ( eidgaah tashrif ley jatey to sabse pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhatey , Namaz se farigh ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ke samney khadey hotey . tamam log apni safon mein baithey rahtey , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein waz (nasihat) w nasihat farmatey, achi baton ka hukm detey. agar jihad ke liye kahin lashkar bhejney ka irada hota to usko alag kartey. kisi aur baat ka hukm dena hota to wo hukm detey. iske baad Shahar ko wapas tashrif laatey. Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke log barabar usi sunnat par qaaim rahe lekin Muawiya ke zamane mein Marwan jo Madina ka Hakim tha phir main uske sath eidul-fitr ya eidul-Azha ki Namaz ke liye nikla ham jab eidgaah pahunchey to wahan maine Kaseer-bin-Salat ka bana hua aik member dekha. jatey hi Marwan ne chaha ke is par Namaz se pahley ( khutba dene ke liye) chadhey isliye maine unka daman pakad kar kheenchaa, lekin wo jhatak kar uper chadh gaya aur Namaz se pahley khutba diya. maine usse kaha ke Allah ki qism tum ne (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sunnat ko) badal diya. Marwan ne kaha ke aey abu-Saeed! ab wo zamana guzar gaya jis ko tum jantey ho. abu-Saeed ne kaha ke b-khudaa main jis zamane ko janta hun us zamane se behtar hai jo main nahi janta. Marwan ne kaha ke hamarey daur mein log Namaz ke baad nahi baithtey , isliye maine Namaz se pahley khutbe ko kar diya."
957,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-Azha aur eidul-fitr ki Namaz pahley padhtey phir Namaz ke baad khutba detey.
958,aapko maine ye kehtey huey suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-fitr ke din eidgaah tashrif le gaey to pahley Namaz padhi phir khutba sunaya.
959,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aik shakhs ko us zamane mein bheja jab (unki khilafat ki shuruaat ka zamana tha aap ne kahlaayaa ke) eidul-fitr ki Namaz ke liye azan nahi di jati thi aur khutba Namaz ke baad hota tha.
960,eidul-fitr aur eidul-Azha ki Namaz ke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Khulafae-Rashedeen ke ahad mein azan nahi di jati thi.
961,"(eid ke din) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey, pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi phir khutba diya, us se farigh ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aurton ki taraf gaey aur unhein nasihat ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath ka sahara liye huey they aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna kapda phaila rakha tha, auratein usmein khairat daal rahi thin. maine is par Ata se puchha ke kya us zamane mein bhi aap imam par ye haq samajhtey hain ke Namaz se farigh honey ke baad wo aurton ke paas aa kar unhein nasihat kare. unhon-ne farmaya ke beshak ye un par haq hai aur sabab kya jo wo aisa na karein."
962,"main eid ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar aur umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sab ke sath gaya hun ye log pahley Namaz padhtey , phir khutba diya kartey they."
963,"Nabi Karim (sl), Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) dono eidon ki Namaz khutbe se pahley padha kartey they."
964,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne eidul-fitr ke din 2 rakatein padhein na unse pahley koi nafl padha na unke baad . phir ( khutba padh kar) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aurton ke paas aaey aur Bilal aap ke sath they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton se farmaya khairat karo. wo khairat dene lagiin koi apni baali pesh karne lagi koi apna haar dene lagi
965,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham us din pahley Namaz padhengey phir khutbe ke baad wapas ho kar qurbani karengey. jisne is tarah kya us ne hamari sunnat ke mutabiq amal kya aur jisne Namaz se pahley qurbani ki to uska zabiha gosht ka janwar hai jisey wo ghar walon ke liye laya hai, qurbani se uska koi bhi talluq nahi. aik Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) jinka naam abu-Barda-bin-Niyaar tha boley ke ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maine to (namaz se pahley hi) qurbani kar di lekin mere paas aik saal ki pathiya hai jo daanti hui bakri se bhi achi hai. aap ne (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya ke achchha usi ko bakri ke badle mein qurbani kar lo aur tumharey baad ye kisi aur ke liye kafi na hogi."
966,main (haj ke din) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha jab neze ki anii aap ke talwey mein chubh gaee jiski wjah se aap ka paon rikaab se chipak gaya. tab maine utar kar usey nikaalaa. ye waqia Mina mein pesh aaya tha. jab Hajjaj ko malum hua jo us zamane mein ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke qatl ke baad Hajjaj ka ameer tha to wo beemar pursi ke liye aaya. Hajjaj ne kaha ke kash! hamein malum ho jata ke kis ne aapko zakhmi kya hai. is par ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke tone hi to mujh ko neza maara hai. Hajjaj ne puchha ke wo kaisey? aap ne farmaya ke tum us din hathiyar apne sath laey jis din pahley kabhi hathiyar sath nahi laya jata tha (eidain ke din) tum hathiyar haram mein laey halanke haram mein hathiyar nahi laya jata tha.
967,Hajjaj Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya main bhi aap ki khidmat mein maujood tha. Hajjaj ne mizaaj puchha Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke achchha hun. us ne puchha ke aapko ye barchha kisne maaraa? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke mujhey us shakhs ne maara jisne us din hathiyar sath ley janey ki ijazat di jis din hathiyar sath nahi ley jaya jata tha. aap ki murad Hajjaj hi se thi.
968,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ke din khutba diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us din sabse pahley hamein Namaz padhni chahiye phir (khutbe ke baad) wapas aa kar qurbani karni chahiye jisne is tarah kya usne hamari sunnat ke mutabiq kya aur jisne Namaz se pahley zabah kar diya to ye aik aisa gosht hoga jisey usne apne ghar walon ke liye jaldi se taiyaar kar liya hai, ye qurbani hargiz nahi. is par mere maamun abu-Barda bin-Niyaar ne khadey ho kar kaha ke ya Rasulullah! maine to Namaz ke padhney se pahley hi zabah kar diya. albatta mere paas aik saal ki aik pathiya hai jo daant nikli bakri se bhi zyada behtar hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iske badle mein usey samajh lo ya ye farmaya ke usey zabah kar lo aur tumharey baad ye aik saal ki pathiya kisi ke liye kafi nahi hogi."
969,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya un dinon ke amal se zyada kisi din ke amal mein fazeelat nahi. logon ne puchha aur jihad mein bhi nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, jihad mein bhi nahi siwa us shakhs ke jo apni jaan w maal khatre mein daal kar nikla aur wapas aaya to sath kuchh bhi na laya (sab kuchh Allah ki raah mein qurbaan kar diyaa)."
970,"maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se talbiya ke mutaalliq malum kya ke aap log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein usey kis tarah kehtey they. us waqt ham Mina se Arafaat ki taraf ja rahe they, unhon-ne farmaya ke talbiya kehney waley talbiya kehtey aur takbeer kehney waley takbeer. is par koi aetraz na karta."
971,(Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaane) mein hamein eid ke din eidgaah mein janey ka hukm tha. kunwari ladkiyan aur haaiza auratein bhi parde mein bahar aati thin. ye sab mardon ke peechhey parde mein rehtin. jab mard takbeer kehtey to ye bhi kehtin aur jab wo dua kartey to ye bhi kartin. us din ki barkat aur pakeezgi hasil karne ki ummeed rakhteen.
972,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney eidul-fitr aur eidul-Azha ki Namaz ke liye barchhi aagey-aagey uthai jati aur wo eidgaah mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney gaad di jati Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usi ki aad mein Namaz padhtey.
973,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidgaah jatey to barchha (dandaa jiske nichey lohey ka phal laga hua ho) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aagey-aagey ley jaya jata tha phir ye eidgaah mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney gaad diya jata aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski aad mein Namaz padhtey.
974,hamein hukm tha ke parde wali ladkiyon ko eidgaah ke liye nikaalein aur Ayub sakhtiyan ne Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se bhi isi tarah riwayat ki hai. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ki hadis mein ye zyadti hai ke ladkiyan aur parde waaliyaan zaroor (eidgaah jaaein) aur haaiza Namaz ki jagah se alehda rahen.
975,maine eidul-fitr ya eidul-Azha ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhney ke baad khutba diya phir aurton ki taraf aaey aur unhein nasihat farmai aur sadqe ke liye hukm farmaya.
976,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-Azha ke din Baqee ki taraf tashrif le gaey aur 2 rakaat eid ki Namaz padhai. phir hamari taraf chehra Mubarak karke farmaya ke sabse muqaddam ibadat hamarey us din ki ye hai ke pahley ham Namaz padhein phir (namaz aur khutbey se) lot kar qurbani karein. isliye jisne is tarah kya usne hamari sunnat ke mutabiq kya aur jisne Namaz se pahley zabah kar diya to wo aisi cheez hai jisey usne apne ghar walon ke khilaaney ke liye jaldi se muhaiya kar diya hai aur uska qurbani se koi talluq nahi. is par aik shakhs ne khadey ho kar arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! maine to pahley hi zabah kar diya. lekin mere paas aik saal ki pathiya hai aur wo daanti hui bakri se zyada behtar hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khair tum usi ko zabah kar lo lekin tumharey baad kisi ki taraf se aisi pathiya jaaiz na hogi.
977,"kya aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath eidgaah gaey they? unhon-ne farmaya ke haan, aur agar bawajud kam Umri ke meri qadr w manzilat aap ke yahan na hoti to main ja nahi sakta tha. aap us nishan par aaey jo kaseer-bin-Salat ke ghar ke qareeb hai. aap ne wahan Namaz padhai phir khutba diya. uske baad aurton ki taraf aaey. aap ke sath Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. aap ne unhein waz (nasihat) aur nasihat ki aur sadqe ke liye kaha, chunanche maine dekha ke auratein apne hathon se Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kapdey mein daley ja rahi thin. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ghar wapas huey."
978,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne eidul-fitr ki Namaz padhi. pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi iske baad khutba diya. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutbe se farigh ho gaey to utrey (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidgaah mein member nahi lekar jatey they. to us utrey se murad buland jagah se utrey (aur aurton ki taraf aaey. phir unhein nasihat farmai . aap us waqt Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke hath ka sahara liye huey they. Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna kapda phaila rakha tha jis mein auratein sadqa daal rahi thin. maine Ata se puchha kya ye sadqa fitr de rahi thin. unhon-ne farmaya ke nahi balke sadqe ke taur par de rahi thin. us waqt auratein apne chhalley ( wghaira) barabar daal rahi thin. phir maine Ata se puchha ke kya aap ab bhi imam par iska haq samajhtey hain ke wo aurton ko nasihat karey? unhon-ne farmaya haan un par ye haq hai aur kya wjah hai ke wo aisa nahi kartey.
979,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath eidul-fitr ki Namaz padhney gaya hun. ye sab hazraat khutbe se pahley Namaz padhtey aur baad mein khutba detey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey, meri nazron ke samney wo manzar hai, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ko hath ke ishaarey se bitha rahe they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safon se guzartey huey aurton ki taraf aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Bilal they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmai ''aey nabii! jab tumharey paas momin auratein bait ke liye aaein''. phir jab khutbe se farigh huey to farmaya ke kya tum un baton par qaaim ho? aik aurat ne jawab diya ke haan. unke ilawa koi aurat na bolii, Hasan ko malum nahi ke bolney wali khatun kon thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khairat ke liye hukm farmaya aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna kapda phaila diya aur kaha ke lao tum par mere maan-baap fidaa hun. chunanche auratein chhalley aur anguthiyan Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kapdey mein dalney lagiin. Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha ( فتخ ( badey ( chhalley ( ko kehtey hain jiska jahiliyat ke zamane mein istemal tha."
980,"ham apni ladkiyon ko eidgaah janey se mana kartey they. phir aik khatun bahar se aai aur qasre-banu-Khalaf mein unhon-ne qiyam kya main unse milney ke liye hazir hui to unhon-ne bayan kya ke unki behan ke shauhar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baara ladaaiyon mein Sharik rahe aur khud unki behan apne shauhar ke sath 6 ladaaiiyon mein Sharik hui thin, unka bayan tha ke ham mareezon ki khidmat kya kartey they aur zakhmiyon ki marham patti kartey they. unhon-ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah! kya ham mein se agar kisi ke paas chadar na ho aur us wjah se wo eid ke din ( eidgaah ( na ja sakey to koi harj hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski saheili apni chadar ka aik hissey usey udha de aur phir wo khair aur musalmanon ki dua mein Sharik hun. Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir jab umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) yahan tashrif laaein to main unki khidmat mein bhi hazir hui aur malum kya ke aap ne falan-falan baat suni hai. unhon-ne farmaya ke haan, mere bap aap par fidaa hun. umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) jab bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr kartin to ye zaroor kehtin ke mere bap aap par fidaa hon, haan to unhon-ne batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jawan parde wali ya jawan aur parde wali bahar niklin. shuba Ayub ko tha. albatta haaiza auratein eidgaah se alehda ho kar baithiin unhein khair aur musalmanon ki dua mein zaroor Sharik hona chahiye Hafsa ne kaha ke maine umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se malum kya ke haaiza auratein bhi? unhon-ne farmaya kya haaiza auratein Arafaat nahi jaatiin aur kya wo falan-falan jaghon mein Sharik nahi hotiin (phir ijtimae-eid hi ki shirkat mein kon si qabahat hai)."
981,"hamein hukm tha ke haaiza aurton, ladkiyon aur parde waaliyon ko eidgaah le jayen ibne-Aun ne kaha ke ya (hadees mein) parde wali ladkiyan hai albatta haaiza auratein musalmanon ki jamat aur duaon mein Sharik hon aur (namaz se) alag rahen."
982,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidgaah hi mein nehar aur zabah kya kartey.
983,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baqar-eid ke din Namaz ke baad khutba diya aur farmaya ke jisne hamari tarah ki Namaz padhi aur hamari tarah ki qurbani ki, uski qurbani durust hui. lekin jisne Namaz se pahley qurbani ki to wo zabiha sirf gosht khaney ke liye hoga. is par abu-Barda bin-Niyaar ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qism Allah ki maine to Namaz ke liye aaney se pahley qurbani kar li maine ye samjha ke aaj ka din khaney peeney ka din hai. isi liye maine jaldi ki aur khud bhi khaya aur ghar walon ko aur padausiyon ko bhi khilaaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bahar-haal ye gosht (khaaney ka ( hua (qurbaanii nahi ( unhon-ne arz kya ke mere paas aik bakri ka saal bhar ka bachcha hai wo 2 bakriyon ke gosht se zyada behtar hai. kya meri ( taraf se uski ( qurbani durust hogi ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, magar tumharey baad kisi ki taraf se aisey bachchey ki qurbani kafi na hogi."
984,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baqara-eid ke din Namaz padh kar khutba diya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis shakhs ne Namaz se pahley janwar zabah kar liya usey dobara qurbani karni hogi. is par Ansar mein se aik sahib uthey ke ya Rasulullah ! mere kuchh ghareeb bhookey padosi hain ya yun kaha wo mohtaaj hain. isliye maine Namaz se pahley zabah kar diya albatta mere paas aik saal ki aik pathiya hai jo 2 bakriyon ke gosht se bhi zyada mujhey pasand hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ijazat de di.
985,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Baaqar eid ke din Namaz padhney ke baad khutba diya phir qurbani ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne Namaz se pahley zabah kar liya ho to usey doosra janwar badle mein qurbaan karna chahiye aur jisne Namaz se pahley zabah na kya ho wo Allah ke naam par zabah kare.
986,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eid ke din aik raaste se jatey phir doosra rasta badal kar aatey. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Yunus bin-Muhammad ne Fulaih se ki, unse Saeed ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya lekin Jaabir ki riwayat zyada sahi hai."
987,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) unke yahan (Minaa ke dinon mein) tashrif laey us waqt ghar mein 2 ladkiyan daf bajaa rahi thin aur Buaas ki ladai ki nazmein ga rahi thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chehra Mubarak par kapda daley huey tashrif farma they Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne un donon ko daantaa. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chehra Mubarak se kapda hata kar farmaya ke Abu-Bakar jaane bhi do ye eid ke din hain (aur wo bhi Mina mein) .
988,maine (eik baar ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey chipa rakha tha aur main Habsha ke logon ko dekh rahi thi jo masjid mein teeron se khel rahe they. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein daantaa lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke janey do aur unse farmaya aey banu-Arfada! tum be-fikr ho kar khel dikhaao.
989,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-fitr ke din nikley aur) eidgaah ( mein 2 rakaat namaze-eid padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne na us se pahley nafl Namaz padhi aur na iske baad . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they.
